text: The 2019 Coastal Carolina Chanticleers men's soccer team represented Coastal Carolina University during the 2019 NCAA Division I men's soccer season and the 2019 Sun Belt Conference men's soccer season. The regular season began on August 30 and concluded on November 9. It was the program's 42nd season fielding a men's varsity soccer team, and their 4th season in the Sun Belt.
